name: Demon Boy: Alexander. White Frame
description:
Traumatized by bullying as a child and betrayed by his family whom he trusted, Alexander became one of the most evil and cunning individual demons on the planet. He was originally a student of Saint Monica’s Religious School, his years of abuse enabled his mind to become corrupted. Seizing up the opportunity, Lucifer himself struck a deal with him to give his life purpose by turning him into a demon.

The Gallery Gehenna Project is a daily art project where there are multiple frames for each individual artwork, each with different types of rarity applied. White frames of Demon Boy: Alexander will be initially exclusively as gifts and giveaways on Twitter and Discord and all artworks will be compatible within the Gallery Gehenna Mobile Game with each artwork unlocking a playable segment.
